reg_forms

Online registration forms project, built with Uni-Form jQuery- and CSS-based 
web form library in a Padrino (Sinatra) application.

Planned features:
- Validate form data for completeness and format
- Validate physical addresses using Yahoo PlaceFinder API
- Incorporate some type of digital signature or attached PDF scans for
  legal agreements
- Auditing (temporal database) based on nightly "AutoComm" and "AutoSend"
  to PowerSchool Student Information System.
  
Resources:
- http://www.cs.arizona.edu/~rts/publications.html on temporal databases
- http://sprawsm.com/uni-form/ Uni-Form forms library
- http://www.padrinorb.com/ Padrino web app framework

